{"tid":1266142,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"侵侵放話會繼續供貨比華為","createTime":"2019-06-29T13:02:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-29T13:27:41.000Z","uid":98232,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b5e46bf90bde734fbc95fe8399918733b693e845","tid":1266142,"uid":98232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T13:02:24.000Z","msg":"連提都無提過香港<br />\n當佢神咁拜既連登仔縮哂入老母西到？"},{"pid":"a26ca1dc51cec41c3c710781e13ab8b3564b9756","tid":1266142,"uid":98232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T13:13:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ec15c6445405607b1e00424e80fd430bb4c9312","tid":1266142,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T13:15:27.000Z","msg":"⋯⋯特朗普在記者會談到華為說，美國公司可以售賣設備給華為，而這些設備是不存重大國家安全問題。（U.S. companies can sell their equipment to Huawei.We&rsquo;re talking about equipment where there&rsquo;s no great national security problem with it）他重申，華為是複雜的議題，會留待之後再說。面對記者多次追問，特朗普說今次沒有與習近平討論華為，但稱下周會就華為是否剔出黑名單討論。被問到有沒有與習近平談到華為首席財務官孟晚舟，特朗普表示沒有。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/article/21709/中美峰會-g20大阪峰會-貿易談判-21709/中美同意重啟談判-美至少目前不加徵新關稅-特朗普：美公司可售華為不涉重大國安問題設備\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Farticle%2F21709%2F%E4%B8%AD%E7%BE%8E%E5%B3%B0%E6%9C%83-g20%E5%A4%A7%E9%98%AA%E5%B3%B0%E6%9C%83-%E8%B2%BF%E6%98%93%E8%AB%87%E5%88%A4-21709%2F%E4%B8%AD%E7%BE%8E%E5%90%8C%E6%84%8F%E9%87%8D%E5%95%9F%E8%AB%87%E5%88%A4-%E7%BE%8E%E8%87%B3%E5%B0%91%E7%9B%AE%E5%89%8D%E4%B8%8D%E5%8A%A0%E5%BE%B5%E6%96%B0%E9%97%9C%E7%A8%85-%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%EF%BC%9A%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E5%8F%AF%E5%94%AE%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA%E4%B8%8D%E6%B6%89%E9%87%8D%E5%A4%A7%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E5%95%8F%E9%A1%8C%E8%A8%AD%E5%82%99&d=raogrMnRIgwaKnbVZhVJo6VJa0bF76%2FliPNifPMhSX0%3D&h=4a05f65b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkcnews.com/article/21709/中美峰會-g20大阪峰會-貿易談判-21709/中美同意重啟談判-美至少目前不加徵新關稅-特朗普：美公司可售華為不涉重大國安問題設備</a><br />\n<br />\nMr. Trump said that any comprehensive resolution of the many issues involved in American legal action against Huawei would not be possible until other bilateral issues have been resolved.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.nytimes.com/2019/06/28/world/asia/g20-summit.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2019%2F06%2F28%2Fworld%2Fasia%2Fg20-summit.html&d=raogrMnRIgwaKnbVZhVJo6VJa0bF76%2FliPNifPMhSX0%3D&h=1e2b52ad\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.nytimes.com/2019/06/28/world/asia/g20-summit.html</a>"},{"pid":"4f16b3ea3c86081abe3fc03db31b0e50dbea3132","tid":1266142,"uid":98232,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T13:27:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}